The paper deals with interference alignment in a MIMO-MAC system with limited feedback, which involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), signal processing (cs.SI), multimedia (cs.MM), and computer communication (cs.COM). However, since the paper focuses on the technical aspects of interference alignment and feedback, cs.IT and cs.NI are the most likely categories. The paper also involves simulations, which could potentially fall under cs.SI or cs.MM. Finally, the paper deals with communication systems, which could fall under cs.COM.
